				<td colspan="2"><span><i>- /melody ability implemented for bards - To use /melody, type /melody . The numbers are the same numbers you would use for the /cast command. The melody will repeat the songs in the specified order until a note is missed due to an interruption. *</i>
<br />

<br />
WTF how many years now has bard been the class for the elite, the vets. the people who cared about taking there time and playing there best. Iv been around since beta and played many bards on many servers, and always played them the best could, busting my a$ to twist 3-4-5 songs a time, and always getting the praise of anyone around me after each fight for not being one of THOSE bards who just sings one song during a fight and another at downtime, Id play anything I could, id twist untill my fingers hurted everynight for my group and guild. now they have ruined it, for me, for you, by making anyone with a hotkey open able to &quot;twist&quot; like the best of us. as of this patch my bard will never be played again, she is remembered as a great bard prepatch and Id like to keep her known as that. before the servers get swarmed with tons of new alt &quot;autobards&quot; to fill the whole that was made due to the fact that it USE TO take skill to play a bard. and the worst thing is.... <i>...missed due to an interruption. *         * Denotes a change requested by the community</i>, WHO the h*ll sujested this???? sure as h*ll not a bard, unless the unskilled ones who made it to level 20 and quit because they felt like losers who couldent twist, or were lazy and getting yelled at. GOD. I use to love my bard, busted my a$ to get epic AND 12aa's before level 52, mastered PoD mass kiting. god, this is the saddest patch ever. the death of bards. /mourn bards.
<br />

<br />
~~~Never forget Dec 15 2004, The day the bard died~~~</span></td>
